summary:
- **General Meeting Results**: All resolutions passed, including:  
  - Ratification of option/share issuances to RiverFort (~93% approval).  
  - Approval of related-party placements to Asimwe Kabunga (89% approval) and Trevor Matthews (93% approval).  
  - Approval of shares issued to directors in lieu of fees (~93% approval).  
  - Special resolution to change company name passed (93% approval).  

*No material trading or capital markets impact identified beyond approval of prior transactions.*
